<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Mon, 25 Apr 2022 05:51:55 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>傳 Twitter 已開始與 Elon Musk 談判，回應股東要求</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/04/25/elonmusktwitter/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=elonmusktwitter</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 25 Apr 2022 05:41:25 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Elon Musk]]></category><category><![CDATA[Twitter]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1097097</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Twitter 董事局一向對 Elon Musk 的收購案持反對態度，但後者已宣佈通過銀行籌集到大額資金，為防 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Twitter 董事局一向對 Elon Musk 的收購案持反對態度，但後者已宣佈通過銀行籌集到大額資金，為防公司被買斷合併（Tender Offer, 指買方在股票市場上公開收購對方公司的股票）形式收購，高層亦無奈改變政策。近日有消息指 Twitter 已展開了同 Elon Musk 的收購談判案。</p><p>在 Elon Musk 的收購案中，他將會以每股 54.20 美元（約港幣 425.27 元）購入 Twitter 股票，比該公司近 1 個月的股價要高出不少。據路透社報道，不少小股東包括擁有 0.15% 股權的投資公司 Kerrisdale Captial Management 都表示，這個收購價相當吸引，指公司應該答應 Elon Musk 的收購案，或作若干還價回應。</p><p>不過亦有股東反對，包括大股東沙地阿拉伯瓦利德 Al Waleed bin Talal，他認為 Twitter 的成長前景，比起 Elon Musk 提出的報價還要高，現時收購價未能顯示出 Twitter 的真正價值。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">I don&#39;t believe that the proposed offer by <a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@elonmusk</a> ($54.20) comes close to the intrinsic value of <a href="https://twitter.com/Twitter?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Twitter</a> given its growth prospects.</p><p>Being one of the largest &amp; long-term shareholders of Twitter, <a href="https://twitter.com/Kingdom_KHC?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Kingdom_KHC</a> &amp; I reject this offer.<a href="https://t.co/Jty05oJUTk">https://t.co/Jty05oJUTk</a> <a href="https://t.co/XpNHUAL6UX">pic.twitter.com/XpNHUAL6UX</a></p><p>&mdash; الوليد بن طلال (@Alwaleed_Talal) <a href="https://twitter.com/Alwaleed_Talal/status/1514615956986757127?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 14, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>Elon Musk 在早前公佈已取得了 9.2% Twitter 股票，成為了該公司最大股東，當時公司建議 Elon Musk 加入董事局，後因各種原因未能成事，後者轉為宣佈收購 Twitter。</p><p>外媒《華爾街日報》則收到消息，指 Elon Musk 的收購案好大機會能取得成功，但收購價將不會少過每股 60 美元（約港幣 470.78 元）。雖然董事局早前推出防止敵意收購的政策，但其後 Elon Musk 宣佈取得大量華爾街銀行貸款，Twitter 董事局為防止公開收購的情況出現，最終也無奈展開談判。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://jp.reuters.com/article/twitter-m-a-musk-investors-exclusive/exclusive-twitter-under-shareholder-pressure-to-seek-deal-with-musk-sources-say-idUSKCN2MG0K7">Reuters</a></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://www.foxbusiness.com/markets/elon-musk-holding-companies-twitter">Foxbusiness</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=PnXIb9Tdr0U:MV8KbpOXzCg:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=PnXIb9Tdr0U:MV8KbpOXzCg:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>微軟拍片示範 Surface 如何拆機，給用戶自行維修權利與資訊</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/04/25/surfacelaptopstudio/notebook/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=surfacelaptopstudio</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 25 Apr 2022 05:11:36 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[流動電腦]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1097078</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Microsoft 發表了一段影片，展示如何為 Surface Laptop Studio 拆機，整個過程拍攝 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Microsoft 發表了一段影片，展示如何為 Surface Laptop Studio 拆機，整個過程拍攝成影片給用家參考，影片中更深入到每一個零件的拆卸技巧。Microsoft 此舉是希望能透過影片，展示其產品的可維修性，以迎合其公司環保政策。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/RWG0dx.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097085" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/RWG0dx-694x260.png" alt="" width="694" height="260" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/RWG0dx-694x260.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/RWG0dx-1280x479.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/RWG0dx-768x288.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/RWG0dx-1536x575.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/RWG0dx.png 1599w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在影片中可看到微軟技術人員從機箱開始，逐步示範如何拆機，並更新機內各項零件。包括 Laptop Studio 的電池，此電池固定在主機板上，但只要翻動易拉片，就可輕鬆拆掉。而影片更示範到用家毋須拆卸主機板，都可更換電池、SSD、熒幕。另外眾多擴展插口如耳機插口，都是模組化配件，例如電腦只壞了耳機插槽，毋須整塊底板更換，只要舊零件拔出，再把新零件裝上去便可。這亦展示了微軟為提升電腦的可維修性，從設計上已經開始考慮到簡化用家自行維修的程序。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Surface-Laptop-Studio-Repair-Video-6-40-screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097083" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Surface-Laptop-Studio-Repair-Video-6-40-screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Surface-Laptop-Studio-Repair-Video-6-40-screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Surface-Laptop-Studio-Repair-Video-6-40-screenshot-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Surface-Laptop-Studio-Repair-Video-6-40-screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Surface-Laptop-Studio-Repair-Video-4-24-screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097084" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Surface-Laptop-Studio-Repair-Video-4-24-screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Surface-Laptop-Studio-Repair-Video-4-24-screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Surface-Laptop-Studio-Repair-Video-4-24-screenshot-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Surface-Laptop-Studio-Repair-Video-4-24-screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Surface-Laptop-Studio-Repair-Video-7-46-screenshot.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Surface-Laptop-Studio-Repair-Video-12-24-screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1097082" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Surface-Laptop-Studio-Repair-Video-12-24-screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Surface-Laptop-Studio-Repair-Video-12-24-screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Surface-Laptop-Studio-Repair-Video-12-24-screenshot-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Surface-Laptop-Studio-Repair-Video-12-24-screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Surface-Laptop-Studio-Repair-Video-6-40-screenshot.jpg"><br /></a></p><p>影片中技術人員指在用家拆下了 SSD 之後，整部電腦的電源就不會意外開啟（除非用戶強行連接外部電源），這也提升了維修電腦時的安全性。</p><p>微軟展示這類拆機影片，展示其電腦的可維修性，近合近年在網路上用家群提倡的自行維修環保理念。除微軟外，愈來愈多科技公司因不同理由，如股東或社會壓力，加強了這方面的發展，例如 Apple 都已經宣佈用戶可自行維修其 iPhone 手機，Apple 將發售個別零件並提供拆解資訊給用戶。</p><p>資料來源：Microsoft YouTube</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_77243"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cnBAeUD0Li4?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p></p><div class="feedflare">
